## ‚ö†Ô∏è Common Errors & Fixes

**Error: "Port 3000 is in use"**
- Normal! Server will use port 3001 instead
- Just use the URL shown in terminal

**Error: "Invalid API key"**
- Check [.env](file:///d:/DevForge%20Ai%20Complete%20Project/.env) file has correct `GEMINI_API_KEY`
- Verify key is active at https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey

**Error: 404 "Model not found"**
- Model name doesn't exist yet
- Try next option in the list

**Error: 400 "Invalid request"**
- Usually means wrong API version (/v1/ vs /v1beta/)
- Try switching between them

